LG gram 2in1Your Creative Canvas From Laptop to Tablet Quickly Converts for Your Needs The touch display easily rotates 360 degrees and transforms from laptop to tablet. The LG gram 2-in-1 instantly adapts to your needs or situation, so it's always ready for ideas, inspiration and business. Ultra-lightweight The LG gram 2-in-1 weighs a mere 2.53 lbs. Expand your creativity, efficiency and productivity wherever you go with this highly versatile yet ultra-lightweight laptop. Full HD IPS Touch Display Better Accuracy for Color and Control Protected with Corning® Gorilla® Glass 6, the 14-inch touch screen is a Full HD (1920x1080) IPS display and delivers clear imagery with outstanding color accuracy. Experience virtually no distortion from any angle. LG Stylus Pen (Wacom AES 2.0) Natural & Free-flowing The LG gram 2-in-1 is equipped with Wacom AES 2.0 Stylus Pen so you can create detailed and intricate work. Whether you're drawing, editing images or writing, the LG Stylus Pen's comfortable grip and 4,096 levels of tilt detection will help you work smoothly and precisely. Nebo® App Ideal for Note-taking Equipped with the Nebo App, you can take notes and jot down ideas via an active pen, whether writing or drawing, and convert your handwriting into text, preserving the layout, colors and styles, as well as diagrams and editable equations. 10th Gen Intel® CPU Applying the Newest CPU Featuring the 10th Gen Intel® Core™ processor, the LG gram 2-in-1 helps you improve work efficiency and boost productivity. The 72Wh Battery Lets You Keep Working With a long battery life and improved performance, you'll have up to 20.5 hours on the fully charged 72Wh battery. Keep working while others look for an AC outlet. Thunderbolt™ 3 Charge, Transfer and Display with One Port The Thunderbolt™ 3 port allows up to a 5K display, data transfer with speeds up to 40Gb/s bandwidth, and charging a connected device without a separate power cable. This is done with a single cable. MIL-STD-810G Proven Durability The full metal body made from the same magnesium alloy used as aircraft material is lightweight and super-strong. It meets the demanding MIL-STD-810G military standard for durability and reliability that checks seven factors from shock and dust to extreme temperatures. Fingerprint Reader The Most Secure Log On With the LG gram 2-in-1 you don't need to remember a password, because the fingerprint recognition allows you to log on or wake your laptop/tablet by touching the power button. Backlit Keyboard No Lights? No Problem Thanks to the backlit keyboard you can keep working even in dark environments by simply touching the power button. The keyboard brightness is easily adjusted for two levels. DTS:X Ultra Dive in Deeper DTS:X Ultra is truly immersive 3D audio and provides the most realistic surround sound experience with speakers or headphones. And its flexible UI allows you to create a custom interface.

Description: Small office desk shell belongs to the prestigious HON 10700 Series that includes wood furniture with distinctive styling, contoured solid-wood accents, user-friendly waterfall-shaped edges and rounded corners. Worksurface and end panels feature top-grade, scratch-resistant, stain-resistant and spill-resistant laminate over durable, 1-1/8" thick, solid-core, high-performance particleboard that resists warping. Hardwood trim is stained to match the Henna Cherry laminate. Formal, full-height modesty panel allows the desk to be used as a stand-alone. Two cord-management grommets in the top route and hide wires and cables. They also serve as anchor points for stack-on storage and organizers. 3/4 right pedestal offers a box drawer and a file drawer. Hangrails in the file drawer allow side-to-side letter-size and legal-size filing and front-to-back letter-size filing. All drawers lock. Adjustable hex leveling glides allow this desk to be easily leveled without lifting the unit.
